                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(center)\">Post Office, <placeName>Harrisburg, Pa.</placeName></p>\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <date>Aug 20 1863</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>To the Editor of Occident and<lb/> American Jewish Advocate</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">\n                <placeName>1227 Walnut St<lb/> Phila</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Sir:â€”Pursuant to instructions from the Post Master Gen-<lb/>eral, I\n                have to inform you that your paper addressed to<lb/>\n                <persName>I Dunkelspiel</persName><lb/> is not taken out, but remains dead in this\n                Office. You will please<lb/> discontinue the same.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(4)\">Yours, &amp;c.,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(5)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">GEORGE BERGNER, P. M.</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p>REASON: Refused</p>"
                  },
